'''Lota''' is a [[Hindi]] word for 'pot'. Though it may refer to any pot, the term is most commonly employed for a container filled with water to facilitate the cleaning of one's anal region after defecation.

The [[Muslim shower]] is a more modern alternative to the lota and is a common bathroom fixture throughout the [[Indian_subcontinent|Indian Subcontinent]] as well as in many [[Arab_states]].

In [[Urdu]] and Hindi, the word ''Lota'' is also colloquially used to refer to a person that switches loyalties, especially from one political party to another.

